description:
Hermit Quest Rifts Playlist ► https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PL7VmhWGNRxKiCS6mm0x-H-iAgR6eVObHw
Hermit Quest Rifts Season 2 is a custom made modded minecraft experience, A last team standing, action packed RPG questing game where natural health regeneration and mining are not possible. To obtain loot and progress players need to find loot crates and explore the world to take on bosses and discover wonderful dungeons. This season introduces rifts, portals that take players to a boss world.

Links!
● Second Channel https://www.youtube.com/c/xisumatwo

Hermit Quest is a Minecraft modpack and map, set in a fantasy time where players find loot, fight mobs, bosses and each other to ultimately stand victorious in the end!
